"Sock Goblins"

Scenes - Instructions, Game, Scoring
Sprites - character, goblin, sock

Character:
  init
    set character image
    set size
    set initial position
    set move speed
  process
    create walk cycle
    if up key pressed
      add move speed to y axis
      use back walk cycle
    if down key if pressed
      subtract move speed from y axis
      use front walk cycle
    if right key is pressed
      add move speed to x axis
      use right walk cycle
    if left key is pressed
      subtract move speed from x axis
      use left walk cycle
